    <div class="body">
        <p>The error message is not set when 'mx' is true. More specifically, in Zend_Validate_EmailAddress::_validateMXRecords Zend_Validate_EmailAddress::_error is never called when getmxrr returns false (i.e. when the domain has no mx entry), thus, although the validation fails no error message is set.</p>

